          "startTime": 33.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 27533.333333399998,
          "startTime": 38.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 28066.6666667,
          "startTime": 39.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 30233.3333334,
          "startTime": 41.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あなたに、あなたに、もらった勇気を\n抱きしめて願う明日へ、誰より眩しいヒカリになるから",
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 19033.333396899998,
          "startTime": 43.4666667302
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "prideを胸にsing out～",
      "startTime": 43.4666667302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん！？　いつからそこにいたんですか！？",
      "startTime": 51.7666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ちょうど夕飯の買い出しから戻ったら\nリビングから琴乃ちゃんの歌声が聴こえてきたのよ",
      "startTime": 58.5999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は月スト単独ライブお疲れ様。琴乃ちゃんの\n『song for you』大盛り上がりだったわね",
      "startTime": 66.8666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……歌うまではちょっと不安もあったんですけど\nファンのみなさんも喜んでくれて本当に良かったです",
      "startTime": 75.1333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんもライブにゲスト出演して下さりありがとう\nございました。『voyage』とても素敵でした",
      "startTime": 82.4999972026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ、あのステージに立たせてくれてありがとう\nそれにしても……偶然って本当にあるのねぇ",
      "startTime": 92.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私も、びっくりしました。お姉ちゃんの誕生日に\nお姉ちゃんがバースデーライブをした会場で……",
      "startTime": 101.300000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "まさか自分がライブをするなんて。きっとお姉ちゃんの\n仕業ですよ！　お姉ちゃんが私達を呼び寄せたんです！",
      "startTime": 108.8083328884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、麻奈ちゃんならやりかねないわね\nステージでなんとなーく麻奈ちゃんの気配を感じたもの",
      "startTime": 117.7999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "私もです！　歌っている時に胸がぼわ～っと温かく\nなってきて……多分一緒に歌ってくれたんだと思います",
      "startTime": 127.2333320618,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13000.000000000015,
          "startTime": 140.2333320618
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "同じくよ！　これは間違いなくあの会場に麻奈ちゃんが\nいたわね。ところで、このノートに書いてあるのは……",
      "startTime": 138.0666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞です。昨日『song for you』を\n歌ったら、私もお姉ちゃんに向けて曲を作りたくなって",
      "startTime": 147.9999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　とっても素敵ね！　どんな曲を贈るのかしら？",
      "startTime": 153.0666662217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "色々考えたんですけど『song for you』の\nアンサーソングになるような歌詞を書いています",
      "startTime": 161.5333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "『song for you』はお姉ちゃんが最後に\n私に贈ってくれた曲だから……その想いに応えたくて",
      "startTime": 167.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、少し行き詰まってるんです。お姉ちゃんが歌詞に\n込めてくれた想いを紐解いて解釈してるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 178.1666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "そうねえ。一人で考えても答えが出ない時は、誰かと\nブレストしてみるのも気分転換になっていいと思うわ",
      "startTime": 189.0666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "夕飯の準備に取り掛かるにはまだ早いし\n私で良ければ、話し相手になるわよ",
      "startTime": 197.0333300273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　それじゃあちょっとだけ\n付き合ってもらってもいいですか",
      "startTime": 203.6333300273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんに任せなさい！　せっかくだし、お茶も淹れて\n美味しいお菓子でも食べながら話しましょうか",
      "startTime": 210.9999905904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "『止めどなくあふれる想いの全てをprideに変えて\nsing out』はあ……このフレーズ天才過ぎる",
      "startTime": 222.0999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さ～ん……歌詞の理解を深めれば深めるほど\n私の書いている歌詞に自信がなくなってきました……",
      "startTime": 236.1999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "どうやったらこんな素敵な言葉が出て来るんですか？\nお姉ちゃんの曲に釣り合う歌詞を書ける気がしません！",
      "startTime": 244.4666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ、落ち着いて。それはクリエイターあるある\nだから。物作りをしていれば誰でもおちいる思考なのよ",
      "startTime": 253.5666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "うう……お姉ちゃんにとって『アイドルとしての\nプライド』って……なんだったんですかね",
      "startTime": 266.0666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "私も麻奈ちゃんに直接聞いたことなかったわね\n{user}君なら知ってるかもだけど",
      "startTime": 274.5333056132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、{user}さんにはなんでも\n話してそうですもんね。今度聞いてみます！",
      "startTime": 279.3333056132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_53_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。あら……？　もしかして、琴乃ちゃんが\n着けてるそのネックレスって麻奈ちゃんとお揃い？",
      "startTime": 288.4666389465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
